{"tid":357833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林子健稱自己曾想私下處理傷勢","createTime":"2017-08-13T09:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T16:01:31.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f18fd90da6d4eb6471104129cdf88aa74328cbdb","tid":357833,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】已報警指自己日前被內地人員帶走的民主黨成員林子健強調，自己的確遭人擄走，亦無就被擄走地點更改口供。對於有人質疑他在脫身後前往食飯、洗衣服，他解釋可能是自己太緊張。<br />\n林子健在社交媒體facebook發表直播談話，並接受網民提問他透露，母親曾勸他不要把事件公開，亦想過私下到私家醫院拔釘，他又透露被擄走的過程中，<span style=\"color: red;\">對方曾經批評自己要求習近平下台</span>，他相信是有人要藉他令公眾產生錯覺，以為事件是出於權鬥。<br />\n林子健又不滿自己在調查過程中，向警方透露的詳情被傳媒披露，已向警方反映。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7779ebc96214f5ccd0a6a797b056a7959fe8b50b","tid":357833,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3672118ebc28323e7fa5bb15a7888278bd991c0d","tid":357833,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"332210839d4c559c8f7767c2d089a7704000cf54","tid":357833,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/234224_e33c165764347fe61be19ac5adb9a132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F234224_e33c165764347fe61be19ac5adb9a132.jpg&h=7baf1d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"774c48dab4047fadb4b74b967af3d9ec8c755e63","tid":357833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他又透露被擄走的過程中，對方曾經批評自己要求習近平下台，他相信是有人要藉他令公眾產生錯覺，以為事件是出於權鬥。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂！依家何俊仁話係權鬥喎！<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁講架屌你！"},{"pid":"fa0009573d2ed61d693233a81e82d37fc3ce8246","tid":357833,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"其實條友係咪有精神病架？<br />\n<br />\n見佢個樣好似就中風咁"},{"pid":"9c30b13f64c6ccef88da42d21c0f55beea4d8736","tid":357833,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實條友係咪有精神病架？<br />\n<br />\n見佢個樣好似就中風咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歪咀既通常都唔係好人<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 葉劉"},{"pid":"5eb1d7288f1789645863b62fd6e6f00f2d12eb48","tid":357833,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"林子健又指，暫不便公開3日前曾來電警告他的內地人士，但指對方是在他過去出任民主黨中委時，已有接觸，事發後他再沒有致電對方，指對方過去自稱身份是來自北京的國安，曾自稱「係中央直接嗰條線」，3日前是用WhatsApp電話與他溝通。"},{"pid":"56f92bd5d1e19408a5a65ee5e52942f92b32826c","tid":357833,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"蓋青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f76d6be3e6356864bbf40259abcf2deae6858c","tid":357833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林子健又指，暫不便公開3日前曾來電警告他的內地人士，但指對方是在他過去出任民主黨中委時，已有接觸，事發後他再沒有致電對方，指對方過去自稱身份是來自北京的國安，曾自稱「係中央直接嗰條線」，3日前是用WhatsApp電話與他溝通。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開名囉<br />\n<br />\n佢點解唔開名? <br />\n<br />\n因為開唔到?"},{"pid":"b83f09d75b4113ff7531bde14d7a2094ae040d8d","tid":357833,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"一早 保持與車輛嘅距離"},{"pid":"3ac4f60f5251acebd66bd7ae3880c270cc73a1d0","tid":357833,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實條友係咪有精神病架？<br />\n<br />\n見佢個樣好似就中風咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歪咀既通常都唔係好人<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 葉劉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/a